After installation, copy the main-script into your path:

sudo cp $HOME/.xbmc/addons/script.xbmcdialog/xbmcdialog /usr/local/bin/xbmcdialog
sudo chmod +x  /usr/local/bin/xbmcdialog

The system-wide packages uses a library for the basic-configuration.
For global install copy it into your python-librara-path:

cp $HOME/.xbmc/addons/script.xbmcdialog/xbmcdialogenv.py /usr/lib/python2.7

The global setup is disabled in the source, but this will change till final release.